<topic id='element_distance_to_margin.description'>
  <title>Description</title>
  <titlealts>
    <searchtitle>Data Element: DISTANCE TO MARGIN - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element" keyref="element_distance_to_margin">DISTANCE TO MARGIN</xref>
 is the distance of the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_tumour">Tumour</xref>
 to the closest relevant margin (the rim of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_tissue">TISSUE</xref>
 around the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_tumour">Tumour</xref>
 or lesion which has been removed) whether the 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition" keyref="business_definition_tumour">Tumour</xref>
 is invasive or non invasive, where the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_ucum_unit_of_measurement">UCUM UNIT OF MEASUREMENT</xref>
 is 
              <i>'Millimetres (mm)'</i>.        </p>
  </div>
